item.title: How do I change the picture of what the skull looks like when Pking?
item.dc:creator: @Slave_Scyth Slave Scyth
item.description:
@Slave_Scyth wrote:

Change the image in your client cache.

If you mean your source is displaying the wrong image for the skull, you might want to look for a method such as ‘isInWilderness’ – I think that might be the method that displays the PK image.
